orts success\", \"from\": 9305, \"to\": 9319}, {\"ngram\": \"the military theorist\", \"from\": 9331, \"to\": 9352}, {\"ngram\": \"war-\\\"a real political instrument\", \"from\": 9381, \"to\": 9413}, {\"ngram\": \"a continuation\", \"from\": 9415, \"to\": 9429}, {\"ngram\": \"political intercourse\", \"from\": 9433, \"to\": 9454}, {\"ngram\": \"a carrying\", \"from\": 9456, \"to\": 9466}, {\"ngram\": \"other means\", \"from\": 9486, \"to\": 9497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Russia and China are, unsurprisingly, the most conspicuous offenders, with the resources and capacity to bend the system to their will.\", \"from\": 9500, \"to\": 9635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9500, \"end\": 9506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.8989737752575124e-15, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 9511, \"end\": 9516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999275232794, \"rank\": 7.212074791054842e-08, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most conspicuous offenders\", \"from\": 9538, \"to\": 9568}, {\"ngram\": \"the resources\", \"from\": 9575, \"to\": 9588}, {\"ngram\": \"capacity\", \"from\": 9593, \"to\": 9601}, {\"ngram\": \"the system\", \"from\": 9610, \"to\": 9620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if they are allowed to have their way, other bad actors will imitate their example.\", \"from\": 9636, \"to\": 9723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their way\", \"from\": 9668, \"to\": 9677}, {\"ngram\": \"other bad actors\", \"from\": 9679, \"to\": 9695}, {\"ngram\": \"their example\", \"from\": 9709, \"to\": 9722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately, WADA's failures will damage the Olympic Games themselves.\", \"from\": 9725, \"to\": 9794, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"WADA's failures\", \"from\": 9737, \"to\": 9752}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 9765, \"to\": 9782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Who wants to watch unfair races or rigged events?\", \"from\": 9795, \"to\": 9844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"unfair races\", \"from\": 9814, \"to\": 9826}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 9837, \"to\": 9843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The commercial machine that powers the Games-namely, the Olympic broadcaster, NBC, and multimillion-dollar sponsors such as Visa, Airbnb, and Coca-Cola-should be alarmed: The value of their investment sinks along with the competition's integrity.\", \"from\": 9845, \"to\": 10091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9923, \"end\": 9926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999964960850317, \"rank\": 3.5039253126269814e-06, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The commercial machine\", \"from\": 9845, \"to\": 9867}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 9880, \"to\": 9889}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic broadcaster\", \"from\": 9898, \"to\": 9921}, {\"ngram\": \"multimillion-dollar sponsors\", \"from\": 9932, \"to\": 9960}, {\"ngram\": \"Visa\", \"from\": 9969, \"to\": 9973}, {\"ngram\": \"Airbnb\", \"from\": 9975, \"to\": 9981}, {\"ngram\": \"Coca-Cola\", \"from\": 9987, \"to\": 9996}, {\"ngram\": \"The value\", \"from\": 10016, \"to\": 10025}, {\"ngram\": \"their investment sinks\", \"from\": 10029, \"to\": 10051}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition's integrity\", \"from\": 10063, \"to\": 10090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics' media and sponsorship partners ought to be acting as a powerful countervailing force on WADA to do its job properly and protect their interests.\", \"from\": 10092, \"to\": 10250, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics' media and sponsorship partners\", \"from\": 10092, \"to\": 10136}, {\"ngram\": \"a powerful countervailing force\", \"from\": 10159, \"to\": 10190}, {\"ngram\": \"WADA\", \"from\": 10194, \"to\": 10198}, {\"ngram\": \"its job\", \"from\": 10205, \"to\": 10212}, {\"ngram\": \"their interests\", \"from\": 10234, \"to\": 10249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The very future of the Olympics-together with its ethos of amity, respect, and fair competition-is at stake.\", \"from\": 10252, \"to\": 10360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The very future\", \"from\": 10252, \"to\": 10267}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 10271, \"to\": 10283}, {\"ngram\": \"together\", \"from\": 10284, \"to\": 10292}, {\"ngram\": \"its ethos\", \"from\": 10298, \"to\": 10307}, {\"ngram\": \"amity\", \"from\": 10311, \"to\": 10316}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 10318, \"to\": 10325}, {\"ngram\": \"fair competition\", \"from\": 10331, \"to\": 10347}, {\"ngram\": \"stake\", \"from\": 10354, \"to\": 10359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How many medals will be stolen from clean competitors by doped athletes-even under the noses of Western and other democratic leaders at this summer's Games in Paris-before those who purport to back the Olympic movement take decisive action?\", \"from\": 10361, \"to\": 10601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10457, \"end\": 10464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5907924334670786e-13, \"text\": \"Western\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"How many medals\", \"from\": 10361, \"to\": 10376}, {\"ngram\": \"clean competitors\", \"from\": 10397, \"to\": 10414}, {\"ngram\": \"doped athletes\", \"from\": 10418, \"to\": 10432}, {\"ngram\": \"the noses\", \"from\": 10444, \"to\": 10453}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer's Games\", \"from\": 10497, \"to\": 10516}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 10520, \"to\": 10525}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic movement\", \"from\": 10559, \"to\": 10579}, {\"ngram\": \"decisive action\", \"from\": 10585, \"to\": 10600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the Olympics are to be more than an arena for great-power games, world leaders need to act and resume their responsibility to back the world anti-doping effort.\", \"from\": 10602, \"to\": 10765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 10605, \"to\": 10617}, {\"ngram\": \"an arena\", \"from\": 10638, \"to\": 10646}, {\"ngram\": \"great-power games\", \"from\": 10651, \"to\": 10668}, {\"ngram\": \"world leaders\", \"from\": 10670, \"to\": 10683}, {\"ngram\": \"their responsibility\", \"from\": 10707, \"to\": 10727}, {\"ngram\": \"the world anti-doping effort\", \"from\": 10736, \"to\": 10764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The soul of fair sports depends upon it.\", \"from\": 10766, \"to\": 10806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The soul\", \"from\": 10766, \"to\": 10774}, {\"ngram\": \"fair sports\", \"from\": 10778, \"to\": 10789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheAtlantic.com \\u00a92026The Atlantic Monthly Group.\", \"from\": 10808, \"to\": 10856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10833, \"end\": 10849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Atlantic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Atlantic Monthly\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Atlantic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Atlantic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 10857, \"to\": 10877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and the GooglePrivacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply\", \"from\": 10879, \"to\": 10967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This site\", \"from\": 10879, \"to\": 10888}, {\"ngram\": \"reCAPTCHA\", \"from\": 10905, \"to\": 10914}, {\"ngram\": \"the Go